| --------- | ---------- | ------------ | -------- | ------------- |
| private   | ✅          | ❌            | ❌        | ❌             |
| default   | ✅          | ✅            | ❌        | ❌             |
| protected | ✅          | ✅            | ✅        | ❌             |
| public    | ✅          | ✅            | ✅        | ✅             |

